description:
Online resources for&nbsp;&quot;RNA modelling with the computational energy landscape framework&quot; 

 Contains a detailed description and input files for the study of the 5&#39; hairpin of RNA 7SK published in: 

 &nbsp; 

 K R&ouml;der, G Stirnemann, AC Dock-Bregeon, DJ Wales, S Pasquali 
Structural transitions in the RNA 7SK 5&prime; hairpin and their effect on HEXIM binding, Nucleic Acids Res. 48 (1), 373-389 

 &nbsp; 

 Requires OPTIM ( http://www-wales.ch.cam.ac.uk/OPTIM/ ), PATHSAMPLE ( http://www-wales.ch.cam.ac.uk/PATHSAMPLE/ ) and an AMBER license.

